---
// En Astro-side
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import VideoScroll from "../components/VideoScroll.astro";
---

<Layout>
    <Header />

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto w-full px-6 flex flex-col">
        <div class="w-full mt-12">
            <h1
                class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-teal-400 text-left tracking-tight animate-fade-in-up"
            >
                About my music
            </h1>

            <div
                class="mt-8 bg-gray-800/20 border border-gray-700/30 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 md:gap-12 shadow-xl backdrop-blur-sm animate-fade-in-up"
            >
                <div class="flex-1 space-y-4">
                    <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-teal-300/90 italic">
                        "Every song tells a story, and the keys are where they
                        begin."
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        I've been immersed in music my whole life. From writing
                        my first raw songs to meticulously crafting intricate
                        piano melodies, creating music is how I capture emotions
                        and share them with the world. Whether it's stripping a
                        famous pop track down to its bare acoustic roots or
                        assembling massive layers in the studio, my goal is
                        always the same: authentic connection.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div
                    class="w-full max-w-[240px] sm:max-w-[280px] md:w-72 shrink-0 relative group"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-teal-500/10 rounded-xl blur-xl group-hover:bg-teal-500/20 transition-all duration-500"
                    >
                    </div>

                    <img
                        src="/pianoplaceholder.png"
                        class="w-full relative z-10 rounded-xl shadow-2xl border border-gray-700/50 group-hover:scale-[1.03] group-hover:border-teal-500/40 transition-all duration-500 object-cover aspect-square"
                        alt="Piano performance portrait"
                    />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex justify-center items-center my-20 w-full">
        <div
            class="bg-gray-800/50 p-1 rounded-full inline-flex relative shadow-inner"
        >
            <button
                id="btn-live"
                class="px-6 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-bold transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer bg-teal-400 text-gray-900 shadow-md"
            >
                Live Performance
            </button>
            <button
                id="btn-prod"
                class="px-6 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-bold transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer text-white hover:text-teal-300"
            >
                Music Production
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto pb-20">
        <div id="content-live" class="block animate-fade-in-up">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-400 mb-4">
                Live Performance
            </h2>
            <p class="pt-4 max-w-2xl text-white leading-relaxed">
                I've been immersed in music my entire life. Whether I'm writing
                original songs or putting my own spin on popular tracks, sitting
                at the piano is where I feel most at home. For me, live
                performance is all about connection—taking a piece of music,
                stripping it down to the keys, and sharing that raw energy and
                emotion with an audience.
            </p>
            <h2
                class="mt-16 mb-8 text-3xl font-bold text-teal-400 text-left animate-fade-in-up"
            >
                Some of the Piano covers I have made
            </h2>
            <VideoScroll />
        </div>

        <div id="content-prod" class="hidden animate-fade-in-up">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-400 mb-4">
                Music Production
            </h2>
            <p class="text-white leading-relaxed pt-4 max-w-2xl">
                While live performance is about the raw energy of the moment,
                the studio is where I get to build an entire sonic world from
                the ground up. Music production allows me to take a single piano
                chord or a fleeting idea and sculpt it into a fully realized
                track. Whether I'm layering instruments, dialing in the perfect
                mix, or experimenting with sound design, the studio is where my
                broader creative vision comes to life.
            </p>

            <h2
                class="mt-16 mb-8 text-3xl font-bold text-teal-400 text-left animate-fade-in-up"
            >
                Listen to my latest tracks
            </h2>

            <div
                class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 w-full max-w-5xl mt-8"
            >
                <iframe
                    style="border-radius:12px"
                    src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/2yliUWZhYKmMKfGBvBYG3P?utm_source=generator"
                    width="100%"
                    height="352"
                    frameborder="0"
                    allowfullscreen=""
                    allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
                    loading="lazy"
                    class="shadow-lg transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02]"
                >
                </iframe>

                <iframe
                    data-testid="embed-iframe"
                    style="border-radius:12px"
                    src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/3xG3HQPV6sYkSrZ6YDCN7v?utm_source=generator&theme=0"
                    width="100%"
                    height="352"
                    allowfullscreen=""
                    allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
                    loading="lazy"></iframe>

                <iframe
                    data-testid="embed-iframe"
                    style="border-radius:12px"
                    src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/77KV71TOuQKxJh0xAqiENG?utm_source=generator"
                    width="100%"
                    height="352"
                    allowfullscreen=""
                    allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
                    loading="lazy"></iframe>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
